    <comment>New package: notify-py, a cross-platform desktop notification library for Python (https://github.com/ms7m/notify-py).
On Linux it uses notify-send (libnotify) with a jeepney/D-Bus fallback. The bundled prebuilt macOS Notificator.app is stripped, and the overly strict upstream loguru&lt;=0.6.0 cap is relaxed (builds and imports fine against current loguru).</comment>
